description: This file contains Data Transfer Object (DTO) classes for notes-related API endpoints, including request and response models for creating, updating, and retrieving notes.

classes.name: NoteCreateRequest
classes.description: DTO for creating a new note containing title and content.

classes.name: NoteUpdateRequest
classes.description: DTO for updating an existing note's optional fields.

classes.name: NoteResponse
classes.description: DTO for returning note details including ID and timestamps.

classes.name: PagedNotesResponse
classes.description: DTO for paginated list of notes.
